article.headline: Jones and Edwards score 18 in North Texas' 84-69 win against East Carolina
article.description: — Rubin Jones and Jason Edwards both scored 18 points as North Texas beat East Carolina 84-69 on Sunday.
article.linkText: Jones and Edwards score 18 in North Texas' 84-69 win against East Carolina

article.story: DENTON, Texas -- — Rubin Jones and Jason Edwards both scored 18 points as North Texas beat East Carolina 84-69 on Sunday. Jones also added six assists for the Mean Green (16-12, 9-7 American Athletic Conference). Edwards shot 6 of 14 (4 for 11 from 3-point range). Robert Allen had 16 points and shot 7 of 9 from the field. The Pirates (14-15, 7-9) were led by Brandon Johnson, who posted 14 points and eight rebounds. RJ Felton added 14 points for East Carolina. In addition, Jaden Walker had 11 points. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
